text: Sébastien Jeanneret (born 12 December 1973 in Le Locle) is a former Swiss football player. He played mostly for Neuchâtel Xamax, Servette FC and FC Zürich.http://fra.worldfootball.net/spieler_profil/sebastien- jeanneret/http://www.nationalsoccerteams.com/v2/player.php?id=17730 He played for Switzerland national football teamhttp://www.super- servette.ch/Doku/nati.pdf and was a participant at the 1996 UEFA European Championship. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1973 births Category:People from Le Locle Category:Swiss footballers Category:UEFA Euro 1996 players Category:FC La Chaux-de-Fonds players Category:Neuchâtel Xamax FCS players Category:Servette FC players Category:FC Zürich players Category:Swiss Super League players Category:Switzerland international footballers Category:Association football defenders
